NOTE: This MIT license applies to the source code only. The repository
intentionally does NOT include the following Bandai-copyrighted assets:

- Card images (downloaded by `scripts/cache_*_images.py`)
- Official rule manual PDFs / FAQ JSON (downloaded by `scripts/scrape_official_*.py`)
- Card text/effect strings within `db/cards.json` (re-creatable via `scraper/scraper.py`)

These assets are obtained from public official sources by the user at runtime
and are not redistributed by this repository.

Tournament deck data under `decks/` is sourced from cardrush.media's public
tournament results (card numbers + counts only, no copyrighted text or images).
